oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ernest Tubb at Billy Boy's (16490)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Tubb, Ernest, 1914-1984;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing the Grand Opening of Nashville Comes to Gettysburg Country Show with Ernest Tubb and the Denny Wade Show at Billy Boy's on June 5. Poster features metal photoplates of Ernest Tubb and Denny Wade. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/27582.
